Package edu.oakland.test Description

The test package contains all of the JUnit test classes being used to build a Java application from classes in the production package.

Each test JUnit test class can contain any number of test methods. The JUnit test classes can be combined into a TestSuite class and executed with one command calling the TestSuite class.
